### Admin routes (used by /admin)

### Admin dashboard stats
GET http://localhost:5173/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### List teachers
GET http://localhost:5173/admin/teachers
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### List students (admin)
GET http://localhost:5173/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Create admin student
POST http://localhost:5173/admin/students
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "username": "student_admin_created",
  "email": "student.admin@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "groupId": 1
}


